Project Title: What are the crime hotspots in metro Chicago?

Team Members: Ray, Basanta, Edwin Banks, James Rogers, Jonathan Richards, Lina Kalala, Nathan Deering, Scott Caldwell, Amrita Gurung

Project Description/Outline: The scope of our research project is to analyze and present data regarding group A (violent) crimes to help the class come to a conclusion on the safest areas of Chicago. 

Research Questions to Answer: Does climate factor in to crime rates? What is the peak time of year for crime? Are the hotspots for crime consistent throughout the year?

Datasets to Be Used: Kaggle-Chicago Crime, Data.gov, Bureau of Justice

Rough Breakdown of Tasks: Data Mining/Cleanup, Coding,
